{"tid":82881,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"longboard jj","createTime":"2017-01-16T09:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T07:23:19.000Z","uid":61965,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d15294456c05921848f05b9a99db841899bb4c13","tid":82881,"uid":61965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:52:21.000Z","msg":"小弟玩開Cuiser board（利申好廢）<br />\n不過為左增加難度同玩多啲style,想買番longboard玩。（dancing為主）<br />\n有冇巴絲打知道係香港邊度有Loaded Bhangra board買？<br />\n定係amazon買好？<br />\n <img src=\"https://holland.pk/6udw0ykq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6udw0ykq&h=3a6cfdaa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f19fbb273a2e36d0e8273c4db1cdc7ac5d95309","tid":82881,"uid":61965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:52:30.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a8ecfd971b10a12a2d7172d048b4570cce32c5","tid":82881,"uid":50911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:12:55.000Z","msg":"玩skateboard啦<br />\n男人老狗玩longboard仲要玩dancing唔係玩downhill<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ca495ccb93ae8304eba88adba3e52fc19a9fa1","tid":82881,"uid":216717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T07:23:19.000Z","msg":"可能係香港第一個最大型既板聚 <br />\n希望今個星期日會見到有踩longboard既你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIg：docksessionhk<br />\nFacebook: DockSession Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1st DockSession in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nDockSession是一個活躍於國際的長板活動組織，我們香港有幸於今年參與其中，並邀請到DockSession聖地牙哥地區代表 @joiskwan 參與這次的長板盛事。<br />\n屆時活動將會有Best Freestyle Lines, Best Tricks等比賽，贏得比賽的朋友可獲豐富的獎品！<br />\n比賽完後更有一些團體小遊戲，讓踩長板的朋友們互相認識及有一個愉快和歡樂的聚會。<br />\n<br />\n活動詳情如下：<br />\n2018年10月21日<br />\n下午3時正<br />\n西九龍文化區大馬路 ※參加者請注意安全，穿戴護具。如有任何損傷，本會概不負責<br />\n※如天氣惡劣，本會或考慮另